<h2>What SEO Workflow Automation Actually Means</h2>
<p>SEO workflow automation is the process of connecting SEO tools and triggering actions without manual intervention. A keyword research finding triggers a content brief. A published article triggers an IndexNow ping. A ranking drop triggers an alert.</p>
<p>The goal is not to remove humans from SEO. It is to remove humans from the repetitive parts so they can focus on strategy and creativity.</p>
<h3>Manual vs. Automated Workflows</h3>
